      <title>日本8月购买美国主权债券数量创纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/japanese-buy-record-amount-of-us-sovereign-bonds-in-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本财务省周二发布的最新国际收支数据显示，在国债价格上涨的推动下，日本基金 8 月份购买了创纪录数量的美国主权债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/japanese-buy-record-amount-of-us-sovereign-bonds-in-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:43:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员重新评估刺激政策押注，中国股市涨势减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-stocks-surge-on-return-from-holidays-as-euphoria-extends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一周假期过后，中国境内股市一度上涨，但由于交易员质疑北京方面推出更多刺激措施的决心，股市一度回落。香港股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-stocks-surge-on-return-from-holidays-as-euphoria-extends</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国刺激计划预期消退，布伦特原油继续跌破 80 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中国出台更多刺激措施的预期消退，布伦特原油跌至每桶 80 美元以下，引发了整个市场的避险情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 23:27:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市涨势减弱，亚洲股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市全球领先，但在一场预计将公布经济刺激措施的重要新闻发布会令投资者失望后，股市涨势失去动力。香港股市暴跌，日元上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 22:34:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受各大城市推出优惠政策推动，中国假期房屋销售大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/china-s-home-sales-jump-during-holiday-as-130-cities-offer-perks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国为振兴房地产市场而采取的最新措施已产生立竿见影的效果，从一周假期期间的销售旺盛和买家兴趣来看，情况并非如此。但反弹能否持续则是另一回事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/china-s-home-sales-jump-during-holiday-as-130-cities-offer-perks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
